inter-soldier-john-wick/ |archive-date=November 9, 2019 |access-date=November 9, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"KolstadBlackCap\">{{Cite web |url=https://heroichollywood.com/black-captain-america-falcon-winter-soldier/ |title='The Falcon and The Winter Soldier' Will Explore Reactions To Black Captain America |last=Villaverde |first=Noah |date=August 30, 2019 |website=Heroic Hollywood |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191109230857/https://heroichollywood.com/black-captain-america-falcon-winter-soldier/ |archive-date=November 9, 2019 |access-date=November 9, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ExpandingUniverse\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.marvel.com/articles/tv-shows/marvel-cinematic-universe-after-avengers-endgame |title=What's Next For The Marvel Cinematic Universe After 'Avengers: Endgame' |last=Dinh |first=Christine |date=November 13, 2019 |website=[[Marvel Entertainment|Marvel.com]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114091331/https://www.marvel.com/articles/tv-shows/marvel-cinematic-universe-after-avengers-endgame |archive-date=November 14, 2019 |access-date=November 14, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OduyeSetPhoto\">{{Cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2019/11/22/marvel-falcon-winter-soldier-set-photos-new-cast-member-adepero-oduye/ |title=New The Falcon And The Winter Soldier Set Photos Reveal New Cast Member |last=Outlaw |first=Kofi |date=November 22, 2019 |website=ComicBook.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191123034426/https://comicbook.com/marvel/2019/11/22/marvel-falcon-winter-soldier-set-photos-new-cast-member-adepero-oduye/ |archive-date=November 22, 2019 |access-date=November 22, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ChiamIshikawaCast\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/the-falcon-and-the-winter-soldier-desmond-chiam-miki-ishikawa-disney-plus-marvel-studios-1202808396/ |title='The Falcon And The Winter Soldier' Adds 'Reef Break' Star Desmond Chiam And 'The Terror's Miki Is